race.comment: The $500,000 The Wave. MISS JOELENE (10) was super impressive taking out the Listed Tails Stakes two back before going down by the narrowest of margins in the Listed Members Mile last time out. Boasts a win over this course and distance and has been racing high on confidence this preparation. Should be right there at the business end. SLY BOOTS (6) hit the line strongly to salute at Randwick at the latest effort and the extra furlong here will suit. Don't dismiss lightly. YOU WAHNG (12) will be better for two runs back and gets up to the right distance range now. Watch for sharp improvement. PORT LOCKROY (1) has been plying his trade in Group and Listed company of late and should appreciate the slight drop back in company here. Include from the low draw. WYMARK (3) is a last-start Caulfield winner who shouldn't be slept on.
